# HR Admin UI FastAPI smoke requests
# Use with VS Code REST Client or HTTPie-style tools.
# Replace {{ADMIN_USER}}/{{ADMIN_PASSWORD}} with credentials from your .env.

### Dashboard landing
GET http://localhost:8000/
Authorization: Basic {{ADMIN_USER}} {{ADMIN_PASSWORD}}
Accept: text/html

### Slots management page
GET http://localhost:8000/slots
Authorization: Basic {{ADMIN_USER}} {{ADMIN_PASSWORD}}
Accept: text/html

### Service health check
GET http://localhost:8000/health
Accept: application/json
